[[File:Impalace.png|thumb|250px|The Palace District]]
The '''Palace District''' was the area of [[Galactic City/Legends|Galactic City]] that contained the [[Imperial Palace/Legends|Imperial Palace]] and [[Ambassadorial habitation pyramid|its outbuildings]], [[Darth Vader's Palace]], and [[Xizor's Palace]].

